• Heritage Oudtshoorn Erfenis se algemene jaarvergadering. Alle lede en belangstellendes word genooi na die vergadering. Hazel Jonker gaan interessante inligting oor die geskiedenis van die historiese Pinehurst deel. 18:00. Pinehurst, Jan van Riebeeckweg, Oudtshoorn. •  The Klein Karoo U.Lab aims to create a space for meaningful conversations, especially with those we don’t normally interact with. The guest is dr David Piedt, whose personal story will be used to practice and develop listening skills.17:30 for 18:00 to 19:45, first floor Prince Vintcent Building (entrance behind Boer & Vark). All welcome. Saturday 20 April
